snippet.textDisplay:
I see outlaw-modded Mustang and Cutlass, in part showing what can be done with modularity once you got the base done. (Nice to see the Cutlass wingclip style put to use. 🙂)
I also see the inescapable reworks for the Glaive and Scythe. (Generally Vanduul ships now all look quite similar.)

BTW, the cinemascope format looks crippled. All the time I wanted to see more content on the top and bottom, and it seems difficult for the makers to fit it all in sometimes, too. 16:9 is great.
